<header class="header">
    <h1>Sport and Calories</h1>
    <p>Discover how sports and physical activities help you burn calories and improve your health!</p>
</header>


<main class="content">
    <section class="introduction">
        <h2>Why is Sport Important?</h2>
        <p>
            Physical activity is essential for a healthy body and mind. By combining proper nutrition
            with regular exercise, you can achieve your health goals. Engaging in sports improves
            circulation, strengthens the heart, and delivers oxygen-rich blood to every cell in your body.
        </p>
    </section>

