    </section>

    <section class="tips">
        <h2>Tips for Getting Started</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Choose a sport you enjoy to stay motivated.</li>
            <li>Start with moderate intensity and gradually increase.</li>
            <li>Stay hydrated and eat a balanced diet.</li>
            <li>Incorporate strength training and flexibility exercises.</li>
            <li>Set realistic goals and track your progress.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</main>



